Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\an8}(*Lingerie  女性內衣)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Lingerie…Run?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\an8}墮天市立學園
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂喂 混進來一個奇怪的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧 這傢伙居然敢穿著衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,像你這種一身晦氣的死宅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.97,0:13:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,早點滾回家去吃你媽的奶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你們居然敢把老娘撇到一邊自己High啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎女王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.75,0:14:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Panty & Stocking
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.62,0:14:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,P P Panty 還有 S Stocking
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯? 你誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,老娘對還沒開苞的包○沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,喲 Geek boy 原來你是包○啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是我 我是Brief啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你 你們都沒有見過就亂說 根本就是誣衊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,小樣 居然裝B
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那給老娘看看證據
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行不行不行 絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在這麼多人的面前脫衣服根本是脫離常識的行為吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,而 而且Panty 一想到被你看到我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:14:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,各位同學們 你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我是本次活動的主辦者 Master G
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,通稱M.G.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎各位今晚光臨Lingerie Run
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Master G!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,最初這項活動只是學生特有的一種抗議運動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但歷經歲月洗滌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如今它已經成為一個單純的Party
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我非常中意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Lingerie Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Master G! Master G!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.52,0:15:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但有一點我希望你們記住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這項活動是為了展現你們年輕人的活力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,以及對這所學園的熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.44,0:15:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,當然你也可以全身心的享受這個活動…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs55}廢話好多啊 你這死老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 有活力是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼各位 預備!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快看啊Stocking 這就是所謂的樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,在男人們胯間的海洋裡遨遊的美麗天使
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.59,0:16:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這香蕉看上去好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂 不許跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,救 救救我啊 Panty
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.42,0:16:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那兩個白癡天使
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,明明沒叫你們來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,就自說自話的跑過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人都變成全裸了?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.19,0:16:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:16:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,毫無疑問 這是惡靈幹的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙是被人們遺棄 失去光彩的內衣們的怨念體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,唯有吞掉地面上所有的內衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs55}這傢伙誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,它的憎恨才會平息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs55}我們走吧 Panty
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧 天使們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,消滅惡靈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,保衛大家的Lingerie Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 什麼 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,實在是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我還是第一次看到可以發生變化的內衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不介意的話 讓我吃掉你們那漂亮的內衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,噁 這傢伙是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! 痛到不行…才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.11,0:17:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,哼 誰讓你不好好整修裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真是丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.51,0:17:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 這次真的…咦 一點都不痛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我的Stripe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,小姑娘 這樣可不行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,對待內衣要小心呵護才行啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs55}Panty
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,住手 住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,E E E E E Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這個內衣實在是太美味了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我感覺渾身充滿了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hasta la vista
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 區區Ghost居然這麼囂張
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,咱們上 Stocking
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 就算是追到地獄我們也要報這內衣被吞的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是怎麼辦呢 就算我們追上它 也沒有武器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此就只有用那一招了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.72,0:18:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那一招?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 小子們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,給我全體倒立
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:19:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 上吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我掄我掄我掄我掄我掄我掄我掄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好小
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好細
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,啞炮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,彎的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你對內衣的眼光真是不敢恭維
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在我這個精益求精的內衣美食家看來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是些不入眼的貨色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,要什麼時候才能追上Panty她們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 是Ghost
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 內褲都用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 居然發現這裡有一個內衣可以當甜品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我還是第一次看到好像從垃圾場裡出來的內衣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要是吃掉這種內衣 肯定會拉肚子的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:19:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Panty 好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.33,0:20:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡還有一條內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,噁 為什麼偏偏是包○死宅的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,也只能將就了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,過來 Brief
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Panty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.12,0:20:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow 好大的槍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼一來肯定沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,彷徨於天地間的迷途之子 誕生於汝心的邪惡之靈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,以包裹聖潔處女…以下省略!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,內褲!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,被拋棄內衣的怨念體居然自己拋棄了內衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,哼 真是諷刺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,又 又被你救了 Panty
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.78,0:20:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,痛痛 好痛的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什麼嘛 結果只是個普通人類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.16,0:20:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,靠 和主人一樣沒用的早○槍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 那邊的小偷天使
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,快把我們的內衣還給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 大家看 那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.92,0:21:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不 是內衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.64,0:21:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.98,0:21:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然世俗總說內衣姿態很不雅很下流
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.45,0:21:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但事實並非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.38,0:21:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你們不覺得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.13,0:21:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,內衣並不單單只是用來遮掩恥部的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,它同時也在包容著治癒著人們頹廢的心靈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.18,0:21:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,總之 我想說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,小小的一件內衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.91,0:21:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,便足以掩蓋你們這點微不足道的怒火
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,至少在我看來就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Master G! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.37,0:21:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我們應該笑對內衣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.64,0:22:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,內衣是福!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.02,0:22:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 M.G.說得很對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.22,0:22:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,只要人們互相以內衣姿態示人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.06,0:22:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,世上也就不會再有紛爭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.12,0:22:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Master G! Master G! Master G!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.87,0:22:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs55}真是搞不懂這群傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.34,0:22:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,跟這群傢伙在一起根本是浪費時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,回家吧 Panty
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.94,0:22:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚 學生們的裸體狂潮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.08,0:22:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,讓墮天市的居民陷入恐慌之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他們的目的到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.27,0:22:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,警方在現場逮捕到可疑的蒙面男性
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.46,0:22:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,想出那種活動的人還真是有夠人渣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.42,0:22:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 說來Garter人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:57.51,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Heaven, please sing for me a song of life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:23:02.52,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Heaven, take me into your skies
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.68,0:23:07.19,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}There's no place here for me to hide my cries
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.19,0:23:10.11,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Night and day I'm missing you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.35,0:23:14.30,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}You're so close (so close)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.43,0:23:17.88,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}And it's you that I believe in (I believe in)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.88,0:23:22.60,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}So close, but far away so far I can't touch
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.60,0:23:26.80,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}I'll hold on, 'cause it's you I love so dearly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.80,0:23:29.81,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}When the rain, the storm and all is up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.85,0:23:32.84,ED_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Caress me with your sweet lullaby

